snippet.title: To the Moon 3 - (Spoof) Trailer
snippet.description:
Something's coming. And it's weird.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1182620/Impostor_Factory/

Impostor Factory is a bonkers time-loop tragicomedy murder mystery sci-fi thriller with multiple casualties and a suspicious cat, from the creator of To the Moon.

Official Page (coming soon):
http://freebirdgames.com/impostor-factory
